&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salesforce Developer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;midlevel Salesforce Developer (Contract)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;based in &lt;strong&gt;Colombia &lt;/strong&gt;to support and extend a highly integrated Salesforce environment. This role is execution focused and ideal for a developer who is comfortable working in an established org, contributing both to day to day support and new development, while collaborating closely with an experienced Salesforce Developer and CRM leadership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;not an entry level role&lt;/strong&gt; and not intended to be a long term architecture owner. The successful candidate will be hands on, pragmatic, and able to work semi independently within clearly defined priorities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
