&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 10 years of progressive finance experience, including at least 2 years in the Vice-President of FP&amp;amp;A role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience operating in a SaaS or subscription-based business model highly preferred, including familiarity with ARR, bookings, retention, and recurring-revenue metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a private equity-ba
